Package productClasses.Inheritances

Class LearningResource

java.lang.Object
productClasses.Product
productClasses.Inheritances.LearningResource
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class LearningResource extends Product implements Serializable
The LearningResource class represents a learning resource product in UniShop. It extends the Product class and includes additional attributes specific to learning resources.
